Walsingham, 1905: 125. Type species: 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Aponoea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Aponoea obtusipalpis" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="obtusipalpis">Aponoea obtusipalpis</taxonomicName>
